                  </hi>. I live with my father, who is a baker. I know the prisoner—I have frequently seen him. On the 1st of February, he brought this cheque to change, about eleven o'clock in the morning—I changed it, and took our bill out of it—I gave him 9<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 3<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., and he went away.</p>
